<topic title="Using the editing toolbar">
	<p>All common formatting tasks are available as buttons in the editing toolbar. The toolbar also allows you to create tables, graphs, links and layout in cards and pages.</p>
	<screenshot alttext="Editing toolbar" src="resources/images/new_editing_toolbar.png" />
	<note>To modify content in "Edit" mode, just right click with your mouse. (This becomes particularly handy for editing links, tables, charts, graphs and other macros.)</note>
